DATA LICENSE (separate from the code above)

The compiled / harmonised dataset distributed with this software
(NFHS_Combined_Database_3to6.xlsx and the files under dashboard/data/) is
released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International licence
(CC-BY-4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The underlying survey estimates are derived from the National Family Health
Survey fact sheets produced by the International Institute for Population
Sciences (IIPS), Mumbai, for the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare,
Government of India, and remain subject to IIPS / Government of India terms.
You must attribute IIPS as the original data source in any reuse.

The India boundary GeoJSON (dashboard/data/india_states.geojson) is derived
from an open community map dataset and is provided for visual reference only;
it is not an authoritative depiction of any boundary.
